ca'),(5,180,'en_us','Care Management','<ul><li><em>American Psychosocial Oncology Society</em>website for patients and caregivers, offering counseling referrals all\r\nover US, and toll free helpline 1.866.276.7443 </li><li>\r\n					<em>Cancare</em></li><li><em>Chemotherapy Information from Chemocare</em></li><li><em>Manage Cancer from Christina\'s Garden</em></li><li><em>Treatment GuidelinesStandard care plans and guidelines for all types of cancers</em></li></ul>','2015-03-11 18:02:47','2015-03-11 18:02:47','15d7d675-342e-497a-a122-2857e5ff7034'),(6,181,'en_us','Reliable Medical Search Engines for Any Disease, Including Cancer','<ul><li><em>WebMD</em>Good consumer-friendly medical search engine. </li><li>\r\n					<em>Infotrac</em>You access this through Cleveland Public Library, using your own library card number. From the\r\nCleveland Public Library homepage, choose \"Do Research\" from the left side menu. Then, in the blank search\r\nspace, type Infotrac. When you click on the result, it will ask for your card number. </li><li>\r\n					<em>PubMed</em>Academic level abstracts from the National Library of Medicine\'s huge database of journal articles.</li></ul>','2015-03-11 18:02:47','2015-03-11 18:02:47','3b5045b6-4026-4fe2-8bfc-ded70f07a354');
